### Apply to become seller
POST http://localhost:8080/api/seller/apply
X-User-Roles: USER

### My store
GET http://localhost:8080/api/seller/me/store
X-User-Roles: SELLER

### Update store profile
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/seller/me/store/profile
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: SELLER

{
  "name": "My Store",
  "bio": "About my store",
  "logoUrl": "http://example.com/logo.png"
}

### Admin - List Applications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/seller/applications
X-User-Roles: ADMIN

### Admin - Approve/Reject Application
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/seller/applications/{{applicationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: ADMIN

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}
